\b0 \
- added possibility to prepare scales: text files that define what clips are in which order on a string. \
	one can change from scale to scale quickly with the foot pedal\
\
- fixed bug where unfolded clips would remain when reloading media.\
- fixed string initialisation when changing scales\
\

