\b Changes in version 3.1.0\
\

\b0 - individual channels can now have luma key transparency. This changes somewhat the mixing behavior. For a description, see http://code.google.com/p/videobass/wiki/Mixing\
- channel displays update more frequently\
\
Bugfixes:\
- fixed copying joystick settings from 4 to 1 and from 1 to 4\
- movie transport mechanism now uses internal quicktime clock, this should render playback speed more reliable\
- fixed bug where thumbnail of first clip would not show\
- fixed bug where a recording slot was added even when no slots are requested\
- live recording should now record at correct framerate\
- clearing recordings works now even when there are spaces in hard disk name \
\

\b Known Issues\
\

\b0 - At the moment, the Application does only work correctly with a screen size of minimum 1920 x 1080 pixels\
- Playback is not optimized yet: frame rate is below optimal (usually between 16 and 20 fps)\
- Playback is only extensively tested for clips in DV-PAL format (720x576 25fps 4:3)\
- Playback is 4:3 only\
